item.title: Energy Podcast: Insights into energy sector performance and outlook for the second half of 2024
item.description:
In this month's energy podcast, Senior Portfolio Manager, Rob Thummel, discusses:

  • S&P climbing 15% and the energy sector standing out, led by strong gains in infrastructure
  • Oil prices rising 6% in June and natural gas surging 48% amid production adjustments and demand spikes
  • Energy infrastructure stocks showing resilience with improved fundamentals
  • OPEC+'s decision to extend production cuts and the operational launch of the Mountain Valley... Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/lVSYQ1b_
